  "title": "Gemmologist | Gemologist | GIA Certification",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Position: Gemmologist Specialist / Manager</strong></li><li><strong>Industry: Precious Gemstones, Rare Gem, Diamonds Collections</strong></li><li><strong>5.5 Work Days, 9-6pm (Mon to Fri) , 9am to 1pm Saturday</strong></li><li><strong>Sunday & PH are off.</strong></li><li><strong>Office near Orchard MRT (Private Sales Gallery & Office)</strong></li><li><li><strong>Basic Salary: $4,500 - $7,000 [ Based on Experience ] + Sales Commission Sharing + 13th Months Bonus + Yearly Bonus [ Depends on Company Performance ]</strong></li></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ol><li>Minimum 5+ years working experience in the retail luxury industry, preferable in a jewellery field.</li><li>Certified Gemmologist (GIA, FGA or other relevant certification) will be added advantage.</li><li>Experience in gem identification, diamond grading. jewellery appraisal or gemological services is a plus.</li></ol><p><strong>Gem Identification and Grading:</strong></p><ol><li>Utilize advanced gemmological instruments and techniques to accurately identify and grade</li><li>gemstones, including diamonds, coloured gemstones and pearls</li></ol><p><strong>Client Consultation:</strong></p><ol><li>Provide expert advice to clients on gemstone selection, care and investment.</li><li>Assist in the selection of gemstone for jewellery design and creation</li></ol><p><strong>Procurement:</strong></p><ol><li>Sourcing and procurement of gemstones.</li><li>Inventory Management Maintain accurate records of gemstone inventory</li><li>Monitor gemstone markets trends and advise on potential investments</li></ol><p><strong>Production:</strong></p><ol><li>Cordinate with designers and workshop on new product development.</li></ol><p>#SCR-carson-cheong</p><p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p><p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p>",
